msgid "[[!meta title=\"Applying security updates\"]]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Security updates provided by the distribution should be applied regularly "
"(e.g. once per week).  For servers running Debian or Ubuntu, please do the "
"following:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' * '
msgid "Login as a user with administrative rights."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' * '
msgid "Execute the following commands:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "\tsudo apt-get update\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "\tsudo apt-get upgrade\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The following software was not installed via the distribution's package "
"system, therefore updates need to be applied manually:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: ' * '
msgid "(none so far)"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"(Please update this list when something new is installed out-of-band.)  For "
"such software it is highly recommended that the administrator / "
"administrative team are subscribed to the announcement mailing list of the "
"respective projects, so that no updates which fix security bugs are missed."
msgstr ""
